Doc: The specification of how the premium for an FX OTC option is quoted.

Source.Contents:
/#
 The specification of how the premium for an FX OTC option is quoted.
 #/
enum FpML5.pretrade.PremiumQuoteBasisEnum {
    # Premium is quoted as a percentage of the callCurrencyAmount.
    PercentageOfCallCurrencyAmount 
    # Premium is quoted as a percentage of the putCurrencyAmount.
    PercentageOfPutCurrencyAmount 
    # Premium is quoted in the call currency as a percentage of the put currency.
    CallCurrencyPerPutCurrency 
    # Premium is quoted in the put currency as a percentage of the call currency.
    PutCurrencyPerCallCurrency 
    # Premium is quoted as an explicit amount.
    Explicit 

}

PercentageOfCallCurrencyAmount.Doc: Premium is quoted as a percentage of the callCurrencyAmount.
PercentageOfCallCurrencyAmount.Name: PercentageOfCallCurrencyAmount

PercentageOfPutCurrencyAmount.Doc: Premium is quoted as a percentage of the putCurrencyAmount.
PercentageOfPutCurrencyAmount.Name: PercentageOfPutCurrencyAmount

CallCurrencyPerPutCurrency.Doc: Premium is quoted in the call currency as a percentage of the put currency.
CallCurrencyPerPutCurrency.Name: CallCurrencyPerPutCurrency

PutCurrencyPerCallCurrency.Doc: Premium is quoted in the put currency as a percentage of the call currency.
PutCurrencyPerCallCurrency.Name: PutCurrencyPerCallCurrency

Explicit.Doc: Premium is quoted as an explicit amount.
Explicit.Name: Explicit
